organic.title: Fairbanks Cancer Care Physicians
organic.snippet: In 2009 the Coxes partnered with Dr. Carroll to form Fairbanks Cancer Care Physicians, PC (FCCP). Dr. Andrew Cox has served as president of FCCP since 2011.

organic.title: Appointments - Fairbanks Cancer Care Physicians
organic.snippet: Appointments can be made by calling our office at 452-4768, or by stopping by the front desk to schedule as you are leaving your visit.

organic.title: About FCCP - Fairbanks Cancer Care Physicians
organic.snippet: At Fairbanks Cancer Care Physicians, we offer compassionate, evidence-based oncology care to residents of Interior Alaska.

organic.title: Support Team - Fairbanks Cancer Care Physicians
organic.snippet: The Clinical Team is comprised of licensed nurses, oncology technicians and medical assistants chosen specifically for their dedication to excellence.
